text:
For complex scripts, save to file.
Create script.awk:
/^ATOM/ {
    count++
    x += $7
    y += $8
    z += $9
}

END {
    print "Atoms:", count
    if (count &gt; 0) {
        print "Avg X:", x/count
        print "Avg Y:", y/count
        print "Avg Z:", z/count
    }
}
Run it:
awk -f script.awk protein.pdb
